title: STRONG MOVEMENT 2015 GALA
desc: Strong Movement Inc. fosters an environment which furthers the development of our representatives and members personal leadership skills. On an annual basis Strong Movement Incorporated will recognize the unique contribution of various community partners, staff, and other professionals who have added to the campaign and fight against diabetes within the community. The 2015 Award Banquet is to be held on Saturday, December 5th, 2015. Invitation to the banquet is extended to all those who support the campaign and fight against diabetes. We encourage everyone to nominate those who are deserving of a Strong Movement Award .
